♪♪

38:02.758 --> 38:04.325
Oh. [ Chuckles ]

38:04.369 --> 38:05.500
Hi.

38:05.544 --> 38:07.763
♪♪

38:07.807 --> 38:09.548
I didn't realize --
I'll go.

38:09.591 --> 38:12.028
Stay.
Nice out here.

38:12.072 --> 38:13.421
It's quiet.

38:13.465 --> 38:16.337
It is.

38:16.381 --> 38:19.253
♪ I don't mind a heavy heart

38:19.297 --> 38:20.559
You know,
I read somewhere

38:20.602 --> 38:22.822
you can see the Northern Lights
from Seattle.

38:22.865 --> 38:24.258
Is that true?

38:24.302 --> 38:27.392
Sometimes.
Very faintly.

38:27.435 --> 38:29.394
[ Sighs ]

38:29.437 --> 38:30.830
♪ 'Cause it's a little bit hard,
a little bit so much ♪

38:30.873 --> 38:32.092
You know everyone was
vetting you tonight.

38:32.135 --> 38:33.528
[ Chuckles ]

38:33.572 --> 38:35.791
Yeah, I mean, I figured
when Maggie was asking me

38:35.835 --> 38:39.055
if I support public television
and the U.S. Postal Service.

38:39.099 --> 38:40.709
It kinda
clued me in a little bit.

38:40.753 --> 38:43.059
[ Laughs ]

38:43.103 --> 38:45.192
♪ I'll hold you tight...

38:45.235 --> 38:46.802
I don't blame them.

38:46.846 --> 38:48.064
♪ ...when you're feeling
lonely ♪

38:48.108 --> 38:49.239
Everybody
loves Meredith.

38:49.283 --> 38:51.981
Yeah.

38:52.025 --> 38:54.636
We're gonna
miss her a lot.

38:54.680 --> 38:56.159
I know.

38:56.203 --> 38:57.596
♪ No matter what,
I'll stick around ♪

38:57.639 --> 39:00.381
Do you have
any questions for me?

39:00.425 --> 39:04.559
♪ Please know I'll be
your one and only ♪

39:04.603 --> 39:08.302
Meredith left
once before.

39:08.346 --> 39:10.913
After my brother died.

39:10.957 --> 39:14.395
She just disappeared
for a year.

39:14.439 --> 39:16.484
She was
hundreds of miles away,

39:16.528 --> 39:19.792
and I have never
felt closer to her.

39:19.835 --> 39:21.054
♪ But you find it somewhere

39:21.097 --> 39:23.448
I knew...

39:23.491 --> 39:27.234
she left because
she was drowning...

39:27.277 --> 39:30.542
in grief and pain
here...

39:30.585 --> 39:32.892
same way that I was.

39:32.935 --> 39:35.111
♪ How it changes color
when you get there ♪

39:35.155 --> 39:37.244
♪♪

39:37.287 --> 39:38.767
♪ Cause it's
a little bit hard... ♪

39:38.811 --> 39:41.030
I think you
make her happy.

39:41.074 --> 39:42.162
[ Chuckles ]

39:42.205 --> 39:44.338
And she deserves
to be happy.

39:44.382 --> 39:45.948
Others would have
been broken

39:45.992 --> 39:49.343
by a fraction
of what she's survived.

39:49.387 --> 39:50.910
♪♪

39:50.953 --> 39:53.739
[ Voice breaking ]
I want her life

39:53.782 --> 39:57.351
to be full
of love and joy.

39:57.395 --> 39:59.614
♪ Know you can cry... [ Breathes deeply ]

39:59.658 --> 40:02.008
My only ask of you...

40:02.051 --> 40:03.139
♪ ...when times get ugly

40:03.183 --> 40:04.924
♪ I'll never go
and let you down ♪

