40:22.550 --> 40:23.508
Hey.

40:23.551 --> 40:25.858
[ Gasps ] Oh.

40:25.901 --> 40:27.555
You're still here.

40:27.599 --> 40:28.991
Yeah,
I'm still here.

40:29.035 --> 40:30.384
[ Sighs ]
I'm sorry I'm so late.

40:30.428 --> 40:32.342
No, no, no, no, no, no.
It's okay.

40:32.386 --> 40:34.475
They're an essential part
of our systems.

40:34.519 --> 40:35.998
What's all this?

40:36.042 --> 40:37.783
Well, I figured
you had a tough case.

40:37.826 --> 40:39.349
Probably didn't
have a chance to eat,

40:39.393 --> 40:41.351
